parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the brake pedal to sink to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.

the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to stop or slow down.
